title: [Circle of Trees, Ground Level]
description: Moonlight dapples the ground between the leaves of the nearby beech tree, touching on the ground around the base.  The floor is uneven here as many roots poke through the soil, creating natural obstacles and pitfalls for those not watching where they are stepping.  Meandering toward the clearing in the center is a thin trail carpeted with fallen leaves.
